Tesó in his drunken state yelled out loud “To our fearless leader Áruló Blackfang!”. “Here here” the clan replies as they yell and cheer, chanting his name aloud. His back being turned looked unto his party with a broken smile... Stood facing the merry group back turned against the sea. With a stoic demeanor... Looked into the eyes of each that were there celebrating. “I hope you can forgive me..”. Proceeds to tear off a pendant that's been around his neck (You can decide what it is if it helps with anything) (Symbolism for some deity and whatnot). Throws it into the fire. 
